<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Feedback Submitted</title>
    <style>
        /* styles.css */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(240, 244, 248, 0.8), rgba(93, 145, 190, 0.8)), url('/LogoUOL.jpg') no-repeat center/cover;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh; /* Full viewport height */
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.2s; /* Smooth hover effect */
        }

        

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s; /* Smooth transition */
        }

        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            transform: translateY(-2px); /* Slight lift on hover */
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }

            .home-button {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 1em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Thank You for Your Feedback!</h1>
        <p>Your feedback has been successfully submitted. We appreciate your input and will use it to improve our services.</p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Go to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>